// Scenario: simple scenario for demonstrating interaction with the
// AutoTPG tool. (The scenario is illustrated in Unify'S D4.3
// document.)

// Query AutoTPG (switch 00:00:00:00:00:00:00:01) every minute,
// extract 'error' from 'result' and display it in a view.
Clock(60)
-> Rest-api(localhost, 8080, /wm/autoTPG/qpc/json,
            {"switch":"00:00:00:00:00:00:00:01","tableid":"0","method":"bin"})
-> Json-filter(result)
-> Json-filter(error) -> view;